  <official_title>A Randomized, Multi-Center, Investigator-Masked, Parallel Group, Equivalence Study of Once Daily Brimonidine Tartrate Ophthalmic Suspension Compared With Three Times Daily ALPHAGAN-PÂ® in Subjects With Open Angle Glaucoma, or Ocular Hypertension</official_title>
