  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study will be conducted to evaluate the efficacy and safety of topical administration of
      brimonidine tartrate ophthalmic suspension compared with brimonidine tartrate ophthalmic
      solution.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
